headline: Invesco Ltd. Announces December 31, 2025 Assets Under Management
summary: Invesco Ltd. (NYSE: IVZ)1, a leading global asset management firm, announced today preliminary month-end assets under management (AUM) of $2,169.9 billion, an increase of 0.7% versus previous month-end. The firm delivered net long-term inflows of $7.7 billion in the month. Non-management fee earning net inflows were $6.1 billion and money market net outflows were $0.7 billion.
